text: Cythara hanleyi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Mangeliidae. This species is considered a nomen dubium. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Samoa. ==References== ==External links== * Tucker, J.K. 2004 Catalog of recent and fossil turrids (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Zootaxa 682: 1–1295. hanleyi Category:Gastropods described in 1888
title: Cythara hanleyi
